
Project-Description (sketch):

A program to (easily) setup & administer several (web-)servers, the focus is on web-application development.

incomplete list of features (some already implemented):
clone (replicate) whole servers/vms/vhosts
access control management
certificate management (ssl/ssh)
debugging
        tools for skimming through logs
        a proxy to inspect communication browser<->application)
deployment
install software (from a list to set up a 'clean' environment)
ssh console/file manager



gtkmozembed.MozEmbed
    found the following bug/undocumented feature: calling render_data() before the widget is realized causes a segfault
